TEXT.description: Take out short separator wall between shower and tub. Take out platform on the left side of the tub - see pic. Leave back platform - this to be reworked with new tiles.  Install new tub up against the left wall. Plumbing for tub will need to be moved to accommodate. Will attach pictures of new tiles and design.

Shower walls and tiles to come out. Replace with all new tiles and one new glass wall across the front of shower area.  New shower will extend forward from its current position about 4-6 inches with just enough room to access small closet.  Shower will also extend to the left by being an open (walk in with no door). Sample photos attached. I have a specific tile design I'd like to use. I'll send tile design info as soon as I've completed.
Replace door with special order door. Door on order, estimated to arrive August 2.
Remove medicine cabinet completely. Seal with drywall.
Paint color = Berh Shiny Luster . Paint all walls this blue/grey color. Trim will be Ultra White.
Vanity cabinet and top will to be replaced. Dark brown cabinet, white and grey marble top, sink bowls to sit on top.
Will be replacing light fixture. Wire for an additional separate fixture = one over each sink. Attaching pic of new fixtures.
